## 5. API Reference

### API Endpoint Table

| No. | Method | Endpoint | Access | Middleware Stack | Description |
|-----|--------|---------|--------|-----------------|-------------|
| 1 | `GET` | `/api/pos/configs` | Manager, Cashier | protect, authorize | List all terminals |
| 2 | `GET` | `/api/pos/configs/:id` | Manager, Cashier | protect, authorize | Get single terminal |
| 3 | `POST` | `/api/pos/configs` | Manager | protect, authorize, validator | Create new terminal |
| 4 | `PUT` | `/api/pos/configs/:id` | Manager | protect, authorize, validator | Rename terminal |
| 5 | `DELETE` | `/api/pos/configs/:id` | Manager | protect, authorize | Soft-delete terminal |
| 6 | `PUT` | `/api/pos/configs/:id/payment-methods` | Manager | protect, authorize | Update payment settings |
| 7 | `POST` | `/api/pos/configs/:id/open-session` | Manager, Cashier | protect, authorize | Open new session |
| 8 | `POST` | `/api/pos/configs/:id/close-session` | Manager, Cashier | protect, authorize | Close current session |
| 9 | `GET` | `/api/pos/configs/:id/sessions` | Manager, Cashier | protect, authorize | Session history (last 10) |

### POST `/api/pos/configs` --- Create Terminal

**Request Body:**
```json
{
  "name": "Odoo Cafe"
}
```

**Server-Side Validation:**

| Field | Rule | Error Message |
|-------|------|--------------|
| `name` | `trim().notEmpty()` | "Terminal name is required" |
| `name` | `isLength({ min: 2, max: 60 })` | "Name must be 2-60 characters" |

**Success Response (201):**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "config": {
    "_id": "662a...",
    "name": "Odoo Cafe",
    "paymentMethods": { "cash": true, "digital": false, "qrPayment": false },
    "upiId": "",
    "lastSessionOpenedAt": null,
    "lastClosingSaleAmount": 0,
    "currentSessionId": null,
    "isActive": true,
    "createdBy": { "_id": "661f...", "fullName": "Deep Patel", "username": "deeppatel" },
    "createdAt": "2026-04-04T09:00:00.000Z",
    "updatedAt": "2026-04-04T09:00:00.000Z"
  }
}
```

### PUT `/api/pos/configs/:id/payment-methods` --- Update Payment Settings

**Request Body:**
```json
{
  "cash": true,
  "digital": true,
  "qrPayment": true,
  "upiId": "odoocafe@upi"
}
```

**Critical Implementation --- Conditional UPI Clearing:**
```javascript
// server/routes/pos.js --- Lines 149-155
if (typeof cash === 'boolean') update['paymentMethods.cash'] = cash;
if (typeof digital === 'boolean') update['paymentMethods.digital'] = digital;
if (typeof qrPayment === 'boolean') update['paymentMethods.qrPayment'] = qrPayment;
if (typeof upiId === 'string') update.upiId = upiId.trim();

// CRITICAL: If QR payment is disabled, automatically clear the UPI ID
if (qrPayment === false) update.upiId = '';
```

This ensures data integrity: when QR payment is toggled off, the UPI ID is automatically purged from the database.

### POST `/api/pos/configs/:id/open-session` --- Open Session

**Request Body:**
```json
{
  "openingBalance": 0
}
```

**Session Guard Logic:**
```javascript
// server/routes/pos.js --- Lines 187-196
// Prevents double-session: checks if an open session already exists
if (config.currentSessionId) {
  const existingSession = await Session.findById(config.currentSessionId);
  if (existingSession && existingSession.status === 'open') {
    return res.status(400).json({
      message: 'A session is already open on this terminal',
    });
  }
}
```

### POST `/api/pos/configs/:id/close-session` --- Close Session

**Close Session Process:**
```javascript
// server/routes/pos.js --- Lines 238-245
session.status = 'closed';
session.closedAt = new Date();
session.closingBalance = req.body.closingBalance || session.totalSales;
await session.save();

config.lastClosingSaleAmount = session.totalSales;
config.currentSessionId = null;  // De-reference the session
await config.save();
```

**Error Responses Across All Endpoints:**

| Status | Condition | Response Message |
|--------|-----------|-----------------|
| `400` | Validation failure | First error message from validator |
| `400` | Session already open | "A session is already open on this terminal" |
| `400` | No session to close | "No active session to close" |
| `400` | Session not open | "No open session found" |
| `403` | Role not authorized | "Role 'cashier' is not authorized to access this resource" |
| `404` | Terminal not found | "Terminal not found" |
| `500` | Server error | "Server error" |

