### State Management Architecture

| State Layer | Tool | Scope | Data |
|-------------|------|-------|------|
| **Page State** | useState | POSConfigurationPage | `configs[]`, `selectedConfig`, `loading`, `refreshing`, `showCreateModal` |
| **Payment State** | useState | PaymentMethodConfigPanel | `cash`, `digital`, `qrPayment`, `upiId`, `saving`, `dirty` |
| **Modal State** | useState | CreatePOSTerminalModal | `name`, `error`, `loading` |
| **Card State** | useState | POSTerminalCard | `showMenu` |
| **Nav State** | useState | TopOperationsNav | `showUserMenu` |
| **Global Auth** | React Context | App-wide | `user`, `isAuthenticated`, `loading` |
| **API Layer** | Axios + Interceptors | Service layer | Token attachment, 401 auto-redirect |

