## 11. Create Terminal Modal Flow

### Modal Lifecycle

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A["Manager clicks 'New Terminal' button"] --> B["showCreateModal = true"]
    B --> C["Modal renders with backdrop blur"]
    C --> D["Auto-focus on name input"]
    C --> E["document.body.overflow = 'hidden'"]
