### Modal Input Validation

| Check | Timing | Condition | Error | UI Element |
|-------|--------|-----------|-------|-----------|
| Empty name | On submit | `!name.trim()` | "Terminal name is required" | Red border + error message |
| Too short | On submit | `name.trim().length < 2` | "Name must be at least 2 characters" | Red border + error message |
| Server error | After API call | `res.status >= 400` | Server error message | Red border + error message |
| Inline clear | On typing | `onChange` fires | Error resets to `''` | Border reverts to normal |

