## 14. Error Handling Matrix

### Complete Error State Table

| Error Type | Source | HTTP | User Sees | UI Treatment |
|-----------|--------|:----:|-----------|-------------|
| Empty terminal name | Client | --- | "Terminal name is required" | Red border + inline error |
| Name too short | Client | --- | "Name must be at least 2 characters" | Red border + inline error |
| Server validation fail | Server | 400 | Server error message | Red border + inline error in modal |
| Terminal not found | Server | 404 | "Terminal not found" | Toast error |
| Session already open | Server | 400 | "A session is already open on this terminal" | Toast error |
| No session to close | Server | 400 | "No active session to close" | Toast error |
| No open session | Server | 400 | "No open session found" | Toast error |
| Role not authorized | Server | 403 | "Role 'cashier' is not authorized..." | Toast error |
| No token | Server | 401 | Auto-redirect to `/login` | Axios interceptor |
| Token expired | Server | 401 | Auto-redirect to `/login` | Axios interceptor |
| Rate limited | Server | 429 | "Too many requests" | Toast error |
| Network failure | Network | --- | "Failed to load terminals" | Toast error |
| Payment update fail | Network | --- | "Failed to update payment methods" | Toast error |
| Unauthorized route | Client | --- | UnauthorizedPage with "Go to My Workspace" | Full page |
| No terminals exist | Client | --- | EmptyPOSState with CTA | Premium empty state |

