## 15. Security Architecture

### Security Measures

| Threat | Protection | Implementation |
|--------|-----------|---------------|
| **Unauthenticated access** | JWT verification | `protect` middleware on all `/api/pos/*` routes |
| **Privilege escalation** | Role-based authorization | `authorize('manager')` on destructive operations |
| **Data visibility leak** | Role-based query filtering | Manager: all; Cashier: `isActive: true` only |
| **UI feature leak** | Conditional rendering | `isManager` flag hides create, settings, toggles |
| **Double session** | Server-side guard | Check `currentSessionId` before creating new session |
| **XSS in terminal name** | Input sanitization | `express-validator` `trim()` + Mongoose schema `trim: true` |
| **Brute force** | Rate limiting | 50 requests / 15 minutes via `express-rate-limit` |
| **CSRF** | SameSite cookie | `sameSite: 'lax'` on JWT cookie |
| **Token theft** | Auto-cleanup | Axios interceptor clears localStorage on 401 |
| **Data integrity** | Auto-clear UPI | When QR toggled off, `upiId` is set to `''` server-side |

### Middleware Stack per Endpoint

```
Every POS route:
  router.use(protect)                         -- JWT verification + user lookup
    router.get(authorize('manager', 'cashier'))  -- Role gate
      handler()                                  -- Business logic
```

---

## 16. Performance Strategy

### Frontend Optimizations

| Strategy | Implementation | Impact |
|----------|---------------|--------|
| **useCallback** on fetchConfigs | Stable function reference | Prevents infinite useEffect loop |
| **Optimistic UI** | New terminal added to state immediately | Zero wait time for user |
| **Selective state merge** | `prev.map(c => c._id === id ? updated : c)` | Only changed card re-renders |
| **Staggered animations** | `animationDelay: i * 80ms` | Smooth visual loading feel |
| **Sticky sidebar** | `sticky top-20` | Sidebar stays visible while scrolling terminals |
| **CSS-only animations** | `transform`, `opacity` | GPU-accelerated, no layout thrash |
| **Conditional rendering** | Modal, Save button, UPI field | Only in DOM when needed |
| **Auto-focus** | `inputRef.current?.focus()` | Instant interaction on modal open |
| **Body scroll lock** | `document.body.style.overflow = 'hidden'` on modal | Prevents background scroll |

### Backend Optimizations

| Strategy | Implementation |
|----------|---------------|
| **Populate only needed fields** | `.populate('createdBy', 'fullName username')` (2 fields, not entire user) |
| **Compound indexes** | `{ posConfig: 1, status: 1 }` for fast session lookups |
| **Session history limit** | `.limit(10)` prevents unbounded queries |
| **Partial subdocument update** | Dot notation `paymentMethods.cash` instead of replacing entire object |
| **Soft-delete** | `isActive: false` instead of `deleteOne()` for data preservation |

---

## 17. Accessibility Support

### WCAG 2.1 Compliance

| Requirement | Implementation |
|-------------|---------------|
| **Keyboard navigation** | All buttons, toggles, cards, and menu items are focusable via Tab |
| **Focus auto-management** | Modal auto-focuses the input field on open |
| **Semantic labels** | Modal input has explicit `<label htmlFor="terminal-name">` |
| **Click target sizes** | Buttons minimum 44px height, cards have spacious tap areas |
| **Color contrast** | Stone-900 on cream-50 = 13.5:1 ratio (exceeds AAA level) |
| **Status indicators** | Not color-only: badge text "Session Active" / "Ready" / "New Terminal" accompanies dots |
| **Toggle accessibility** | Toggle buttons have visible ON/OFF text state for non-managers |
| **Reduced motion** | `prefers-reduced-motion` disables all animations globally |
| **Modal backdrop** | Click backdrop to dismiss, plus visible X close button |
| **Event propagation** | `e.stopPropagation()` prevents card selection when clicking buttons inside cards |

